{"tid":948223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"永別了《櫻桃小丸子》　完結篇聖誕節發行","createTime":"2018-12-20T01:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T18:48:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"492c94925291ed234a9e41926a9ad8f9af9b306c","tid":948223,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181219/640_a29e89c69c96d7309576cc37f3ce0e2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181219%2F640_a29e89c69c96d7309576cc37f3ce0e2b.jpg&h=6eb85592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著日本國民漫畫家櫻桃子在8月乳癌離世，櫻桃子的名作《櫻桃小丸子》也成為絕響，出版商「集英社」宣布，將在12月25日聖誕節這天，發行《櫻桃小丸子》完結篇第17卷，為《櫻桃小丸子》畫下完美句點。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《每日新聞》報導，在《櫻桃小丸子》完結卷中，並沒有櫻桃子的新作品，而是收錄過去未在單行本刊登的全7集漫畫，包括25周年紀念「神奇的魔法卡」特別版、電視動畫「小丸子弄丟存摺篇」，以及30周年紀念創作的「小丸子憧憬夏威夷篇」。<br />\n<br />\n《櫻桃小丸子》從1986年在少女漫畫雜誌《Ribon》開始連載，之後成為日本國民漫畫，多年下來共賣了超過3200萬本，並被改成電視動漫，無論是大人還是小孩，《櫻桃小丸子》可謂當代最有人氣漫畫之一。"},{"pid":"24c0f405c738df4533ba8bf3f82ddc546c1dedbf","tid":948223,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:24:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"132ba805603e36d9ea2253480df500cc7ccb1a47","tid":948223,"uid":31208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:33:37.000Z","msg":"三十年先出得17卷⋯"},{"pid":"05404c6bac2ac7ab6c7ed97b190c86af946244dd","tid":948223,"uid":16326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:34:17.000Z","msg":"1986年發行<br />\n最小32歲"},{"pid":"a28ec4486fdb2906efc1a9d8d47ba2a7058baed9","tid":948223,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"132ba805603e36d9ea2253480df500cc7ccb1a47","tid":948223,"uid":31208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:33:37.000Z","msg":"三十年先出得17卷⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"動畫先癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n龍珠,叮噹,小新四十幾期都出得幾百集動畫<br />\n佢17期一樣出到幾百集"},{"pid":"49eb9821df1b0ff5fd97cb1dc9e2fc196b0216cb","tid":948223,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"應該會好似叮噹咁<br />\n漫畫唔再出<br />\n但係動畫keep住出 ?"},{"pid":"6d31dd1f0fb4d2f6070271dcd4eee824af6ad00b","tid":948223,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49eb9821df1b0ff5fd97cb1dc9e2fc196b0216cb","tid":948223,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"應該會好似叮噹咁<br />\n漫畫唔再出<br />\n但係動畫keep住出 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T18:48:31.000Z","msg":"新版動畫畫得小丸子太善良<br />\n舊版畫得佢仆街啲 搞笑好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加埋無綫配得佢全家夠抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}